question: Ellen is required to submit a 232-page report. She already finished writing 1/2 of the report. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Ellen has already written 1/2 of the report which is 232 pages*1/2 = <<232*1/2=116>>116 pages.
So, she still needs to write 232 pages - 116 pages = <<232-116=116>>116 pages.
#### 116
